<section class="content">
  <div class="container  ">
    <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
      <div class="contact-form-warp">
        <h4 class="comment-title">CREATE AN ACCOUNT</h4>
        Creating an account using this form, will automaticly create you a login for our forums. You will be able to login with the same username and password.
        <br /><Br />
        <form class="comment-form">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <h6 class="form-label">Username</h6>
              <input type="text" placeholder="✎">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <h6 class="form-label">Email Address</h6>
              <input type="email" placeholder="✎">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h6 class="form-label">Password</h6>
              <input type="password" placeholder="✎">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <h6 class="form-label">Confirm Password</h6>
              <input type="text" placeholder="✎">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
              <button class="site-btn btn-sm centered">Send</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

